  "texts": [
    "For instance, it enables the investigation of specific historical individuals by inputting their names, the examination of corresponding historical events by inputting relevant keywords, and the exploration of the evolution of philosophical concepts in academic discourse.",
    "Diachronic N-gram Vicissitude on the 2000-year timeline.",
    "Human language is constantly changing with the evolution of society, giving rise to new vocabulary while phasing out old ones.",
    "These transformations manifest in the usage frequency of texts, often mirrors specific cultural phenomena of a particular historical epoch.",
    "The Evol platform provides a diachronic statistical function for n-grams, which allows users to investigate the frequency change of n-grams across different eras through line charts."
